{"tid":1556352,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[抵制黨鐵] 我不支持跳閘, 希望用其他手法抗爭","createTime":"2019-09-09T16:36:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T00:20:01.000Z","uid":41458,"like":49,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"9b9426c7bda773c39e3ebf7fe59c56068e09bd87","tid":1556352,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:36:23.000Z","msg":"跳閘, <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">成本低但效益亦都低, 而且風險高</span></strong><br />\n開頭跳閘成功人當然多, 但當跳閘成為常態<br />\n黨鐵一定會有反制措施, 加派人手睇住閘機, 叫埋黑警裡應外合<br />\n就算現場走甩, 難保佢地癲起上嚟睇CCTV捉人<br />\n所以<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>不支持跳閘</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我地對黨鐵既 <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">戰略目標, 係要佢收入大幅減少</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n其實係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">完全合法</span></span>情況下, 仍然有好多野做到<br />\n1. 最簡單, 盡可能<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔坐黨鐵</strong></span>, 轉坐巴士<br />\n2. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對黨鐵廣告商狙擊</span></strong>, 罷買, 就好似狙擊CCTVB一樣. 可以先對落最貴廣告既入手, 重點, 目標唔好太多, 火力每次集中三個目標以內. (例如香港站超大型屏幕廣告)<br />\n3.  黨鐵係外國都有投資, 例如瑞典既鐵路, 大家上去留言, <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">呼籲外國停止繼續使用MTR提供既服務</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">(留言理據參考原因: 支持民主人權, 有證據顯示黨鐵同極權政府合作打壓香港人民)</span><br />\n4. 黨鐵既鐵路, 列車, 維護車站等, 其實有好多既供應商, 特別係外國. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">呼籲外國停止為MTR提供服務/零件, 又或者拒絕同MTR續約</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n(各位自己發揮創意, 歡迎補完)<br />\n<br />\n好多意見方法我都係睇各位手足既POST綜合返嚟<br />\n全部合法!"},{"pid":"27a5b3c6c14f1bfcaf1b201f243c7de9e63bfaf1","tid":1556352,"uid":254330,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:40:06.000Z","msg":"你唔支持ok,但你唔好叫其他人唔好跳...<br />\n兄弟爬山"},{"pid":"5b9e9705c9653b2166c5999403a504e079727ba9","tid":1556352,"uid":2904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:40:40.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山 各自努力！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[全民和你唱]</span></span> 全世界全天候街邊唱香港國歌！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1556100\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1556100</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f997f12af69ceb29708f7caace13c88271b29838","tid":1556352,"uid":239812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:55:17.000Z","msg":"有冇話邊d零件特別貴"},{"pid":"2d6cfc5bf747d6dbefb587e4883c085dfe02fdb9","tid":1556352,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:07:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"844651e5e04808b0a6406c11f83e26986ba55627","tid":1556352,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f997f12af69ceb29708f7caace13c88271b29838","tid":1556352,"uid":239812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:55:17.000Z","msg":"有冇話邊d零件特別貴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:17:09.000Z","msg":"方向正確"},{"pid":"b59b861c1d122378fb21b337a91e35c5a3294884","tid":1556352,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:17:49.000Z","msg":"有電腦係入面嘅機特別貴"},{"pid":"69cee17b16ca56c86b48d2cb4190bf16c3c95b53","tid":1556352,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b9426c7bda773c39e3ebf7fe59c56068e09bd87","tid":1556352,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:36:23.000Z","msg":"跳閘, <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">成本低但效益亦都低, 而且風險高</span></strong><br />\n開頭跳閘成功人當然多, 但當跳閘成為常態<br />\n黨鐵一定會有反制措施, 加派人手睇住閘機, 叫埋黑警裡應外合<br />\n就算現場走甩, 難保佢地癲起上嚟睇CCTV捉人<br />\n所以<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>不支持跳閘</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我地對黨鐵既 <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">戰略目標, 係要佢收入大幅減少</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n其實係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">完全合法</span></span>情況下, 仍然有好多野做到<br />\n1. 最簡單, 盡可能<span style=\"color: red;\"><stro