352,"uid":244318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"655472bc7f64bb7dd03e135b3351b39468a7270e","tid":1556352,"uid":255637,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:24:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你個個星期六日 就去港鐵商場坐 罷買  玩佢一頭半個月 佢班商戶自自然然會屌柒狗鐵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:28:25.000Z","msg":"但係見班藍絲個個都係blame the victim先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />d商戶應該都會掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:30:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你係到坐 叫下口號  商場又唔會叫防暴   如果佢叫完防暴就仲衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地既目的係要減少佢收入姐<br />\n<br />\n狗鐵商場既鋪 全部都有業務分成  即係找10蚊除左你要交租之外 仲要俾多幾蚊狗鐵<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總之一蚊都唔好用起狗鐵既商場同鋪 就岩啦"},{"pid":"2dabc32236ee01c3f72d722fdba12864202ca58b","tid":1556352,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b9426c7bda773c39e3ebf7fe59c56068e09bd87","tid":1556352,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:36:23.000Z","msg":"跳閘, <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">成本低但效益亦都低, 而且風險高</span></strong><br />\n開頭跳閘成功人當然多, 但當跳閘成為常態<br />\n黨鐵一定會有反制措施, 加派人手睇住閘機, 叫埋黑警裡應外合<br />\n就算現場走甩, 難保佢地癲起上嚟睇CCTV捉人<br />\n所以<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>不支持跳閘</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我地對黨鐵既 <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">戰略目標, 係要佢收入大幅減少</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n其實係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">完全合法</span></span>情況下, 仍然有好多野做到<br />\n1. 最簡單, 盡可能<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔坐黨鐵</strong></span>, 轉坐巴士<br />\n2. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對黨鐵廣告商狙擊</span></strong>, 罷買, 就好似狙擊CCTVB一樣. 可以先對落最貴廣告既入手, 重點, 目標唔好太多, 火力每次集中三個目標以內. (例如香港站超大型屏幕廣告)<br />\n3.  黨鐵係外國都有投資, 例如瑞典既鐵路, 大家上去留言, <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">呼籲外國停止繼續使用MTR提供既服務</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">(留言理據參考原因: 支持民主人權, 有證據顯示黨鐵同極權政府合作打壓香港人民)</span><br />\n4. 黨鐵既鐵路, 列車, 維護車站等, 其實有好多既供應商, 特別係外國. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">呼籲外國停止為MTR提供服務/零件, 又或者拒絕同MTR續約</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n(各位自己發揮創意, 歡迎補完)<br />\n<br />\n好多意見方法我都係睇各位手足既POST綜合返嚟<br />\n全部合法!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:35:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a14NDGA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa14NDGA.png&h=b89ad2c6&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KL7GH8h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKL7GH8h.png&h=85dd15fd&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HEYe28i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHEYe28i.png&h=4c7ba601&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aw6Xgt9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Faw6Xgt9.jpg&h=be74ca58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n提撚晒水<br />\n大家識做啦<br />\n搞親共商家嘅威力會比圍狗屋大好多倍<br />\n<br />\n因為我哋係用行動方式直接懲罰啲出賣香港人長遠利益嘅機構<br />\n要佢哋知道我哋香港人唔係好蝦！😡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/